data.description: This lovely 3 bedroom ranch located in Park Place Village has so much to offer. This home needs a little bit of love but could be a great home to raise a family and create lasting memories in. The basement rec. room has kitchen, wet bar, & bonus room , large patio, fenced yard, central air, encl. porch. Appliances in 'As Is' Condition.  Off Street parking as well.  Call Philip Wayne Smith to day to see it 570-441-3580
